==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*ἀγάπη / agapē / ag-ah'-pay
*From G25; love, that is, affection or benevolence; specifically (plural) a love feast

===Noun===
'''ἀγάπη'''

# (feast of) [[charity]] ([-ably]), [[dear]], [[love]].

